dc_description_s: This data represents zoning in Bayfield County in 2021 and includes the layers 'BAYFIELD_AIRPORT_2021', 'BAYFIELD_GENERAL_2021' and 'BAYFIELD_SHORELAND_2021'. [For SHORELAND: This layer contains shoreland zoning data for Bayfield County. For GENERAL: This layer contains zoning district data for Bayfield County. For AIRPORT: This layer contains airport location data in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/892/GIS-Data-Access
